<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Austin's Gun Puns</title>
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #2c2c2c;
            color: #f0f0f0;
            background-image: url('https://www.publicdomainpictures.net/pictures/270000/velka/post-apocalyptic-city.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
        }
        #banner {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.7);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
        }
        #pun-container {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        #generate-pun {
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 18px;
            cursor: pointer;
            background-color: red;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        #generate-pun:hover {
            background-color: darkred;
        }
        #pun {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="banner">Austin is a Bitch!</div>
    <div id="pun-container">
        <button id="generate-pun">Generate Joke</button>
        <div id="pun"></div>
    </div>

    <script>
        const puns = [
            "Austin thinks he's a sharpshooter, but he's more like a BB gun at a sniper competition.",
            "When Austin says he's packing heat, he's talking about his microwave dinner.",
            "Austin's idea of a big bang theory is when he pops a balloon.",
            "Austin once tried to join a militia, but they said his Nerf gun didn't qualify.",
            "Austin's gun obsession is like his love life—full of misfires.",
            "Austin says he's ready for the apocalypse, but he can't even handle a water gun fight.",
            "Austin's aim is so bad, he couldn't hit the broad side of a barn with a bazooka.",
            "Austin's favorite gun is the one in his imagination, because it's the only one where he hits the target.",
            "Austin's shooting skills are like his jokes—both miss the mark.",
            "Austin thinks he's a badass, but he still sleeps with a nightlight.",
            "Austin's favorite movie is 'Die Hard,' but he cries during the opening credits.",
            "Austin's idea of heavy artillery is carrying two water pistols.",
            "Austin once tried to go hunting, but the deer laughed at him.",
            "Austin's idea of self-defense is calling his mom.",
            "Austin's favorite sound is his own voice saying 'pew pew' when he plays with his toy guns.",
            "Austin's shooting range nickname is 'Spray and Pray.'",
            "Austin's gun collection is like his love life—nonexistent.",
            "Austin once tried to join the army, but they told him to stick to video games.",
            "Austin thinks he's tough, but he still cries during thunderstorms.",
            "Austin's favorite workout is lifting his ego.",
            "Austin says he's a crack shot, but he can't even crack an egg.",
            "Austin's idea of a high-caliber weapon is a super soaker.",
            "Austin's aim is so bad, he'd miss a target if it was right in front of him.",
            "Austin thinks he's a marksman, but he's more like a marks-missed.",
            "Austin's favorite sport is dodgeball, because he's used to missing.",
            "Austin's idea of a tactical advantage is hiding behind his mom.",
            "Austin once tried to shoot a can, but the can shot back.",
            "Austin's favorite superhero is Deadpool, because he wishes he was that cool.",
            "Austin thinks he's a cowboy, but he wouldn't survive a day in the wild west.",
            "Austin's favorite holiday is the Fourth of July, because he gets to play with sparklers.",
            "Austin's idea of a sniper is someone who hides and still misses.",
            "Austin once tried to join a shooting competition, but he got disqualified for crying.",
            "Austin's favorite animal is a chicken, because he's too scared to be anything else.",
            "Austin thinks he's a warrior, but he's more like a worrier.",
            "Austin's favorite game is hide and seek, because he's good at hiding from reality.",
            "Austin's idea of a big gun is a potato cannon.",
            "Austin once tried to shoot a target, but he shot himself in the foot instead.",
            "Austin thinks he's tough, but he can't handle spicy food.",
            "Austin's favorite type of gun is the one that doesn't exist.",
            "Austin's idea of a battle is arguing with his mirror.",
            "Austin once tried to impress a girl with his gun collection, but she laughed and walked away.",
            "Austin thinks he's a legend, but he's more like a bedtime story.",
            "Austin's idea of a duel is playing rock, paper, scissors.",
            "Austin once tried to shoot a fly, but the fly outsmarted him.",
            "Austin thinks he's a hunter, but he couldn't catch a cold.",
            "Austin's favorite book is 'How to Pretend You're Tough.'",
            "Austin thinks he's a hero, but he's more like a sidekick.",
            "Austin's idea of a big fight is arguing with his little sister.",
            "Austin once tried to scare someone with his gun, but they just laughed."
        ];

        document.getElementById('generate-pun').addEventListener('click', () => {
            const randomPun = puns[Math.floor(Math.random() * puns.length)];
            document.getElementById('pun').innerText = randomPun;
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
